### Hadith 2:733

*Narrated Ibn 'Umar:*

The Prophet offered the Maghrib and 'Isha' prayers together at Jam'
(i.e. Al-Muzdalifa) with a separate Iqama for each of them and did not
offer any optional prayer in between them or after each of them.

